Usage: ctd_save_view [-help] -file <string> [-id <string>] [-legend_on]
                     [-type {PNG GIF}]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>     # File Name. (string, required)
-id <string>       # Win ID, the default value is the returned value of command
                   # get_ctd_win_id. (string, optional)
-legend_on         # Save whole window. (bool, optional)
-type {PNG GIF}    # Type of saved file. The default format is PNG.
                   # (enum, optional)